p: The essential oil compositions of B. erythrophloia, B. robusta, and B. yunnanensis are compiled in Table 2. All three of the Beilschmiedia leaf essential oils were dominated by sesquiterpene hydrocarbons. A preponderance of sesquiterpene hydrocarbons has been previously seen in Beilschmiedia leaf essential oils from Malaysia [ 33] and from Costa Rica [ 34].
